Package pacman.model

This package defines the basic model of the game, including the maze, direction and the coordinate.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coordinate
    This class represents an ADT of a (x,y) coordinate of an agent in the board.
    Maze
    This class is an ADT that represents a pacman map.
    MazeFactory
    A class used to construct a maze, either from local file or from a string.
    MazeFactory.PreConfiguredMaze
    Contains preconfigured mazes.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Direction
    Represents a direction of moving in the maze.
